---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Главная
  order: 1
---
{% set apps = metadata.apps %}
<h1>Популярные {% if apps.length == 1 %}приложение{% elif apps.length == 2 or apps.length == 3 or apps.length == 4 %}приложения{% else %}приложений{% endif %}</h1>

<div class="apps-grid">
  {% for app in apps %}
  <a href="{{ app.url | url }}" class="app-card">
    <img src="{{ app.icon }}" alt="{{ app.title }}" class="app-icon">
    <div class="app-info">
      <h2>{{ app.title }}</h2>
      <p class="app-developer">{{ app.developer }}</p>
      <p class="app-description">{{ app.description }}</p>
      <div class="app-meta">
        <span class="app-rating">{{ app.rating }} ★</span>
        <span class="app-size">{{ app.size }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<p>Больше приложений можно найти в <a href="{{ '/posts/' | url }}">каталоге</a>.</p>